The paper deals with the integration of abductive logic programs and logic program updates, which are both topics related to artificial intelligence and logic programming. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.PL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses tabling techniques, which are commonly used in logic programming and can be related to cs.LO (logic in computer science). Additionally, the paper mentions the representation and reasoning about knowledge changes, which can be related to cs.DB (databases) and cs.SE (software engineering).
